    "description": "MATCH is a minimalist, arcade-style score-attack game that puts the focus on player skill. Memorize, flip, and match cards as you progress through levels, each with a shorter time limit. Compare your high-scores with friends' in the variety of game modes to see who is the MATCH Master!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Memorize, Flip, MATCH</h2>Hone your skill at the minimalist game-play loop; memorize the cards, flip them over, then match them from memory. Each level has a time limit which will get shorter as you progress. How far can you go?<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3083620/extras/979c8d7878cf6f1aaa99e03e8bb24a99.poster.avif?t=1723812542\" width=316 height=184 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3083620/extras/979c8d7878cf6f1aaa99e03e8bb24a99.webm?t=1723812542\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3083620/extras/979c8d7878cf6f1aaa99e03e8bb24a99.mp4?t=1723812542\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Different Modes</h2>Test yourself in the variety of different modes, ranging from focused variants that allow you to practice specific skills to special modes that completely change the game!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3083620/extras/aad3dafad8c7cfa8dfd9daad278cda09.poster.avif?t=1723812542\" width=316 height=184 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3083620/extras/aad3dafad8c7cfa8dfd9daad278cda09.webm?t=1723812542\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3083620/extras/aad3dafad8c7cfa8dfd9daad278cda09.mp4?t=1723812542\" type=\"video/mp4\">